OL,5, The government should not cut taxes in 
OL,6, the upcoming Budget, unless it can     
OL,7, spell out how it will afford them, a   
OL,8, leading think tank has warned.         
OL,10,FThe chancellor has hinted he would like
OL,11,Fto lower taxes in what could be the    
OL,12,Flast Budget before a general election. 
OL,14,FBut the Institute for Fiscal Studies   
OL,15,F(IFS) said the case for tax cuts was   
OL,16,F"weak".                                
OL,18,FThe government said it would not       
OL,19,Fcomment on whether further cuts to tax 
OL,20,Fwould be "affordable in the Budget".   
